{
  "texts": [
    "(d) Text Classification: NER can be used as a feature in text classification tasks.",
    "By identifying and categorizing named entities, the model can gain a deeper understanding of the text, which can improve classification accuracy.",
    "For example: classifying news articles based on the organizations mentioned in them.",
    "(e) Social Media Analysis: NER is valuable for analyzing social media data.",
    "It can help in extracting and categorizing entities such as people, locations and organizations to understand trends, sentiments and user demographics."
  ]
}